text: Rexha is a surname of Albanian origins. Notable people with this name include: *Bebe Rexha (born 1989), American singer and songwriter *Ervin Rexha (born 1991), Albanian footballer *Fitnete Rexha (1933–2003), Albanian folk singer ==See also== *Kënga e Rexhës, a ballet whose title means Rexha's song Category:Surnames Category:Albanian-language surnames
title: Rexha
